WEBVTT

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:02.616
you and Maya Angelou are not the only
two people that this happened to" --

00:05:02.640 --> 00:05:04.776
because I really did
believe that as a child.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:08.136
I had read "I Know Why
the Caged Bird Sings"

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:12.176
and it was the first time I saw
somebody else who had had this experience,

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:17.376
and so I spent a good deal of my childhood
thinking this only happens in books

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:19.016
and in my life.

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:20.616
And it was completely isolating,

00:05:20.640 --> 00:05:22.896
so if somebody had said,

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:25.576
"It's unfortunate but it does
happen to a lot of people;

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.936
you're not alone,"

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:28.616
that would have changed my life.

00:05:28.640 --> 00:05:30.896
And so very early on,